  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/4987880903228f748c53ebc3d198e6b0.poster.avif?t=1728890050\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/4987880903228f748c53ebc3d198e6b0.webm?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/4987880903228f748c53ebc3d198e6b0.mp4?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DiggerSim is a thrilling excavator and heavy equipment simulator that puts you in the driver's seat of a powerful excavator. With realistic controls, you'll feel like you're really operating heavy machinery.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Excavator Movement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You have total control over your excavator that mimic the real thing. The realistic movement dynamics will make you feel as like you're operating heavy machinery. Every motion, including arm swings, was created to provide a genuine and enjoyable experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/8a051d27c4a8b1e0158f399654ffa793.poster.avif?t=1728890050\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/8a051d27c4a8b1e0158f399654ffa793.webm?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/8a051d27c4a8b1e0158f399654ffa793.mp4?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Refined Player Control</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our new Refined Player Control system now supports three control types—SAE, ISO, and Easy Mode—catering to both seasoned operators and newcomers. Additionally, enjoy the flexibility of adjustable seating for a more immersive and personalized experience. Take command with enhanced precision and comfort as you tackle every excavation task with confidence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/003ae07c70de3c21bdba1a81bb9a6cf4.poster.avif?t=1728890050\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/003ae07c70de3c21bdba1a81bb9a6cf4.webm?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/003ae07c70de3c21bdba1a81bb9a6cf4.mp4?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VR Joystick Control</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate your excavator effortlessly using the VR joystick, bringing a new level of immersion and control to your excavation experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/eca29247ac2dcc466aacb305868a3a6a.poster.avif?t=1728890050\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/eca29247ac2dcc466aacb305868a3a6a.webm?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/eca29247ac2dcc466aacb305868a3a6a.mp4?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Excavation Tasks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you'll be tasked with completing a variety of excavation jobs, from digging foundations to clearing land. You'll have to carefully maneuver your excavator through tight spaces and navigate around obstacles to complete the level. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, you'll challenges that will test your skills and abilities. With immersive gameplay and realistic controls, Digger Sim is the ultimate experience for fans of construction and heavy machinery. So put on your hard hat and get ready to dig in!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/4987880903228f748c53ebc3d198e6b0.poster.avif?t=1728890050\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/4987880903228f748c53ebc3d198e6b0.webm?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/4987880903228f748c53ebc3d198e6b0.mp4?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DiggerSim is a thrilling excavator and heavy equipment simulator that puts you in the driver's seat of a powerful excavator. With realistic controls, you'll feel like you're really operating heavy machinery.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Excavator Movement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You have total control over your excavator that mimic the real thing. The realistic movement dynamics will make you feel as like you're operating heavy machinery. Every motion, including arm swings, was created to provide a genuine and enjoyable experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/8a051d27c4a8b1e0158f399654ffa793.poster.avif?t=1728890050\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/8a051d27c4a8b1e0158f399654ffa793.webm?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/8a051d27c4a8b1e0158f399654ffa793.mp4?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Refined Player Control</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our new Refined Player Control system now supports three control types—SAE, ISO, and Easy Mode—catering to both seasoned operators and newcomers. Additionally, enjoy the flexibility of adjustable seating for a more immersive and personalized experience. Take command with enhanced precision and comfort as you tackle every excavation task with confidence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/003ae07c70de3c21bdba1a81bb9a6cf4.poster.avif?t=1728890050\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/003ae07c70de3c21bdba1a81bb9a6cf4.webm?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/003ae07c70de3c21bdba1a81bb9a6cf4.mp4?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VR Joystick Control</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate your excavator effortlessly using the VR joystick, bringing a new level of immersion and control to your excavation experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/eca29247ac2dcc466aacb305868a3a6a.poster.avif?t=1728890050\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/eca29247ac2dcc466aacb305868a3a6a.webm?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254830/extras/eca29247ac2dcc466aacb305868a3a6a.mp4?t=1728890050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Excavation Tasks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you'll be tasked with completing a variety of excavation jobs, from digging foundations to clearing land. You'll have to carefully maneuver your excavator through tight spaces and navigate around obstacles to complete the level. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, you'll challenges that will test your skills and abilities. With immersive gameplay and realistic controls, Digger Sim is the ultimate experience for fans of construction and heavy machinery. So put on your hard hat and get ready to dig in!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
